name: Abdominal Crunch

name: Leg Raise
coach: Exhal when lifting your legs and inhal when lowering.

name: Sit Ups

name: Plank

name: Reverse Crunch
coach: Don't let your elbows reach your knees. Exhale when lifting and inhale when stretching out.

name: Side Plank
coach: Keep your body straight. Don't forget to breathe.

name: Long Arm Crunch
coach: Keep your neck relaxed. Your feet should always stay on the floor. Exhale when lifting and inhale when stretching out.

name: Cobras
coach: Tighten your abdominals when pushing up your chest.

name: Bird Dog
coach: Keep your stretched arm and leg parallel to the floor. Don't wobble your body.

name: Bridge
coach: Hold this position as long as you can. Don't forget to breathe.

name: Mountain Climber
coach: Do it as fast as you can.

name: Cross Arm Crunch
coach: Keep your neck relaxed. Your feet should always stay on the floor. Exhale when lifting and inhale when stretching out.

name: One Leg Bridge
coach: Keep your spine straight when lifting your hips. Exhale when lifting and inhale when lowering.

coach: Inhale when your feet are apart and Exhale when coming back to the start position.

name: Wide Arm Push Up

name: Curtsy Lunge
coach: Exhale when you go down and inhale when you go up.
